  "title": "Tapping for \"is it wrong to want this?\"",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for releasing guilt about wanting wealth.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 15 of Rebecca's MONEY program. The script targets the guilt that arises around wanting more money, the fear of being seen as greedy, selfish, or of having too much.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
